text: Teays Valley ( ) is a census-designated place (CDP) in Putnam County, West Virginia, United States. The place is divided into the two districts of Teays Valley and Scott Depot./aldata20/st54/work/2KGUENT_424_FPLC_5479545/COFPLC_5479545_002 The population was 14,350 at the 2020 census. ==References== Category:Census- designated places in West Virginia
